comments: VanVleet (TOR) makes marginal contact with Sexton's (CLE) wrist during the drive that does not affect his ability to gather the ball.
Sexton (CLE) makes marginal contact with Lowry (TOR) during the play at the basket.  Lowry's (TOR) reaction is not consistent with the level of contact.
VanVleet (TOR) establishes his screening position in Nance's (CLE) path and they briefly engage and disengage.
Replay review of the foul called on Siakam (TOR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Nance beats Siakam to the spot and absorbs the contact on his drive to the basket.
Lowry (TOR) briefly engages with Nance Jr. (CLE) off-ball but does not affect his FOM.
Lowry (TOR) makes contact with Garland's (CLE) arm during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Ibaka (TOR) sets the pick in Sexton's (CLE) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Ibaka (TOR) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Sexton (CLE) makes marginal contact with Powell (TOR) as Powell intercepts the pass on the perimeter.
Lowry (TOR) makes marginal contact with Nance Jr. (CLE) off ball that does not affect his ability to get to the pass.
Sexton (CLE) moves laterally into Powell's (TOR) path in the backcourt and affects his SQBR.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Porter Jr. C(LE) is last to touch the ball before it goes out of play.
Ibaka (TOR) briefly grasps Nance Jr.'s (CLE) opposite side before releasing during the inbound.
Porter Jr. (CLE) commits a take foul on Powell (TOR).
Sexton (CLE) commits a take foul on Siakam (TOR).
Powell (TOR) cleanly dislodges the ball from Sexton (CLE) before making incidental contact with Sexton's body in the backcourt.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Sexton's (CLE) leg is last to touch the ball before it goes out of play.
